{"tid":2239885,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"六旬富婆經營淫網九年收入達6,600萬 認罪 胡雅文裁定判囚三年","createTime":"2020-10-12T09:49:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T11:09:28.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"d258a81cc5c7bd97e5d9c08f1c19fa9c8016889b","tid":2239885,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T09:49:39.000Z","msg":"年輕時曾任陪酒及妓女、婚後居於半山豪宅的六旬婦，開設及營運淫網，並安排家中兩名菲傭接聽客人電話，安排俄羅斯及委內瑞拉等不同國籍妓女到酒店提供上門性服務，九年間營業額估計高達6,600萬元。警員多次放蛇，搗破淫網。涉案六旬婦及其中一名菲傭早前承認串謀依靠他人賣淫收入為生及洗黑錢罪，今分別被判監3年及7個月。<br />\n<br />\n法官胡雅文判刑指，首被告黃佩𤧟（68歲）為案中主腦，辯方早前求情指她有焦慮及抑鬱症狀，惟相關症狀在她營運賣淫網站前已存在；而且被告並非第一時間認罪，即使她聲稱候審期間承受很大精神壓力，亦屬咎由自取。法官考慮到被告年齡、淫網規模、被告所得的財政利益等，就依靠賣淫收入及她承認的三項洗黑錢罪，判監三年。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201012/Q7R6V7JWCRFZ3I4FP2NOHJAX3E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201012%2FQ7R6V7JWCRFZ3I4FP2NOHJAX3E%2F&d=aqHBcmSoErOqRK7CI6xlBbPkHgDHOcRHwLuXI7BMvHI%3D&h=ba7c506b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201012%2FQ7R6V7JWCRFZ3I4FP2NOHJAX3E%2F&h=60e2965c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201012/Q7R6V7JWCRFZ3I4FP2NOHJAX3E/</a>"},{"pid":"78730da608704b9e2cfb35f6fefd214135e5eee3","tid":2239885,"uid":76804,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T09:50:20.000Z","msg":"警員多次放蛇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c63cfa512835997dcf5b36b1beee10609dddc9eb","tid":2239885,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"78730da608704b9e2cfb35f6fefd214135e5eee3","tid":2239885,"uid":76804,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T09:50:20.000Z",